snippet.title: Sonic 30th Anniversary - Master System
snippet.description:
For 30 years of Sonic The Hedgehog!
Thanks for all the amazing moments in my childhood! I dedicate this project to new generations of fans.

- Download games: https://sonic-sms-remake.blogspot.com
- Music from teaser trailer of Sonic Mania
